data.description: This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with an open floor plan that includes a Sunroom, Living Room, Dinning Area and Kitchen.  There is a 1 car detached garage with the laundry space located within it.  Large and enclosed backyard that could serve well for entertaining, an opportunity to explore updates and landscaping or a possible ADU in the future.  The long driveway offers off-street parking and security of access by a motorized gate entry.  The location of the property allows for access to local shops, restaurants and notable entertainment destinations that could be a short drive away, such as Sofi Stadium, The Kia Forum, YouTube Theater.  Downtown Los Angeles is a short drive in the opposite direction by way of Interstate 110.
